===============================================================================
Bravura — SMuFL music font (Steinberg Media Technologies GmbH)
===============================================================================

`crates/render-ireal/src/bravura.rs`, `crates/render-html/src/bravura.rs`,
and `packages/react/src/bravura-glyphs.ts` contain SVG `<path>` outlines
extracted from the Bravura font (https://github.com/steinbergmedia/bravura).
Currently exposed glyphs:

  - U+E047 SEGNO            (render-ireal)
  - U+E048 CODA             (render-ireal)
  - U+E4C0 FERMATA ABOVE    (render-ireal)
  - U+E050 G CLEF           (render-html, @chordsketch/react)
  - U+E262 ACCIDENTAL SHARP (render-html, @chordsketch/react)
  - U+E260 ACCIDENTAL FLAT  (render-html, @chordsketch/react)
  - U+E0A4 NOTEHEAD BLACK   (@chordsketch/react)

These outlines are derivative works of Bravura and are redistributed
under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1 — the same terms as the
upstream Bravura font.

